text: Ahmed Jassim Al-Maqabi (born 26 October 1994) is a Bahraini handball player for Barbar Club and the Bahraini national team. He participated at the 2017 World Men's Handball Championship.2017 World Championship roster ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Bahraini male handball players
